nglish_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"Choi Hui-seung","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Choi Hui-seung","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"崔希胜","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"崔希勝","primary":false}}]}},"person_5957931_translations":{"at":1772689437104,"data":{"id":5957931,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"MX","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Modi Abdullah","primary":true}}]}},"person_1082509_translations":{"at":1772689439378,"data":{"id":1082509,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Takehiro Hira (平 岳大, Hira Takehiro, born July 27, 1974) is a Japanese theatre, film, and television actor.\n\nHira was born in Setagaya, Tokyo, Japan, to actors Mikijirō Hira and Yoshiko Sakuma. He was raised in Japan until he was 15 years old. He went to high school at Moses Brown School in Providence, Rhode Island, United States, and then attended Brown University.\n\nHe made his theatrical debut in 2002 with Rokumeikan, which was written by Yukio Mishima. He worked closely with his father, Mikijirō Hira, who was also a Japanese actor. Takehiro played the role of Iago in the production of Othello with his father playing Othello. He received major recognition when he played the last shogun, Yoshinobu Tokugawa, in the NHK taiga drama Atsuhime. He has appeared in several films of Takashi Miike, including Hara-Kiri: Death of a Samurai, Ace Attorney, and Aku no Kyoten. He plays Natsuka Masaie in the big-budget film Nobou's Castle.\n\nHe played the role of the Player Queen in the English stage production of Hamlet in 2005, in which the title role was played by Michael Maloney. This three-month tour was received well at many places in the UK.\n\nHira played the lead role in the 2019 British TV series Giri/Haji. He has also had notable parts in the American films Lost Girls & Love Hotels (2020) and Snake Eyes (2021) and a minor role in Gran Turismo. In 2024, Hira starred in FX's adaptation of Shōgun.\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Takehiro Hira, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.","name":"Takehiro Hira","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"平岳大","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Такэхиро Хира","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"히라 타케히로","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"平嶽大","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"平岳大平（Takehiro Hira，1974年7月27日-），日本戏剧、电影和电视演员。他出生在日本，在那里长大，直到15岁。他在美国罗德岛州普罗维登斯上高中，然后就读于布朗大学。在成为演员之前，他从事过几种不同类型的工作，包括自闭症儿童的护理提供者、金融分析师、一家互联网初创公司的项目经理和一家日本餐厅的天妇罗主管","name":"平岳大平","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"Takehiro Hira ist ein japanischer Theater-, Film- und Fernsehschauspieler. Frühes Leben und Ausbildung Hira wurde in Setagaya, Tokio, Japan als Sohn der Schauspieler Mikijirō Hira und Yoshiko Sakuma geboren. Er wuchs bis zu seinem 15. Lebensjahr in Japan auf. Er besuchte die Moses Brown School in Providence, Rhode Island, USA, und besuchte dann die Brown University. Karriere Sein Theaterdebüt gab er 2002 mit Rokumeikan, das von Yukio Mishima geschrieben wurde. Er arbeitete eng mit seinem Vater Mikijirō Hira zusammen, der ebenfalls ein japanischer Schauspieler war. Takehiro spielte die Rolle des Jago in der Produktion von Othello, wobei sein Vater Othello spielte. Große Anerkennung erhielt er, als er den letzten Shogun Yoshinobu Tokugawa in dem NHK-Taiga-Drama Atsuhime spielte. Er hat in mehreren Filmen von Takashi Miike mitgewirkt, darunter Hara-Kiri: Death of a Samurai, Ace Attorney und Aku no Kyoten. Er spielt Natsuka Masaie in dem Big-Budget-Film Nobou's Castle. Internationale Erfahrung Er spielte 2005 die Rolle der Player Queen in der englischen Bühnenproduktion von Hamlet, in der Michael Maloney die Titelrolle spielte. Diese dreimonatige Tour wurde an vielen Orten in Großbritannien gut aufgenommen. Hira spielte die Hauptrolle in der britischen Fernsehserie Giri/Haji von 2019. Er hatte auch bemerkenswerte Rollen in den amerikanischen Filmen Lost Girls & Love Hotels (2020) und Snake Eyes (2021) sowie eine Nebenrolle in Gran Turismo. Im Jahr 2024 spielte Hira die Hauptrolle in der FX-Adaption von Shogun.","name":"Takehiro Hira","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Hira nació en Setagaya, Tokio, Japón, hijo de los actores Mikijirō Hira y Yoshiko Sakuma.​ Se crio en Japón hasta los 15 años. Fue al instituto en la Moses Brown School de Providence, Rhode Island, Estados Unidos, y después asistió a la Brown University.","name":"Takehiro Hira","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Takehiro Hira","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Takehiro Hira est un acteur japonais de théâtre, de cinéma et de télévision. Wikipédia","name":"Takehiro Hira","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"تاكاهيرو هيرا (مواليد 27 يوليو 1974) ممثل ياباني في المسرح والسينما والتلفزيون. وُلد في سيتاغايا، طوكيو لعائلة فنية، حيث كان والده ميكيجيرو هيرا ووالدته يوشيكو ساكُوما ممثلين. نشأ في اليابان حتى سن 15، ثم انتقل إلى الولايات المتحدة حيث درس في مدرسة موسى براون في رود آيلاند، ثم التحق بجامعة براون.\n\nبدأ مسيرته المسرحية عام 2002 بمسرحية روكوميكان لـيوكيو ميشيما، وحقق شهرة واسعة بدوره كآخر شوغون، يوشينوبو توكوغاوا، في دراما NHK التاريخية آتسوهيمي. شارك في عدة أفلام لـتاكاشي ميكي، منها Hara-Kiri: Death of a Samurai وAce Attorney وAku no Kyoten، كما لعب دور ناتسوكا ماسايي في فيلم Nobou's Castle. في 2019، أدى دور البطولة في المسلسل البريطاني Giri/Haji، وظهر في أفلام أمريكية مثل Lost Girls & Love Hotels (2020) وSnake Eyes (2021) وGran Turismo. عام 2024، شارك في بطولة مسلسل Shōgun على شبكة FX.","name":"تاكاهيرو هيرا","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Такехіро Хіра","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"平嶽大（Takehiro Hira，1974 年 7 月 27 日-），日本戲劇、電影和電視演員。他出生在日本，在那裏長大，直到 15 歲。他在美國洛迪文島州普羅維登斯上高中，然後就讀於布朗大學。在成為演員之前，他從事過幾種不同類型的工作，包括自閉症兒童的護理提供者、金融分析師、一家互聯網初創公司的項目經理和一家日本餐廳的天婦羅主管","name":"平嶽大","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Takehiro Hira","primary":false}}]}},"tv_91143_credits":{"at":1772689441636,"data":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":107775,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Zhang Jiayi","original_name":"张嘉益","popularity":0.9107,"profile_path":"/sWyVhE0CQgx4BLlabEFH8bplD9i.jpg","character":"Yang Shu","credit_id":"5dcf5d4cb76cbb0011780b0f","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":131303,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Yan Ni","original_name":"闫妮","popularity":0.9064,"profile_path":"/gwH4M0wc6NQHPuWrhaNTOCLpUaK.jpg","character":"Tang Hong","credit_id":"5e587c8ea6d93100185f19c8","order":1},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":1590275,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Maggie Jiang","original_name":"江疏影","popularity":1.1345,"profile_path":"/l